extends java.lang.Object
implements ToGenerator<com.jnape.palatable.lambda.adt.choice.Choice7<A,B,C,D,E,F,G>>
    A builder to facilitate the construction of Generators that yield Choice7 values.

    Use one of the or(dev.marksman.kraftwerk.Weighted<? extends dev.marksman.kraftwerk.Generator<? extends H>>) methods to add more choices, and call toGenerator() to build the final Generator.

    All instances of ChoiceBuilder are immutable and can be reused, even after calling toGenerator.
